{
  "stem": "3964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was in a-- in a work program, which lived in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In other words, I still lived with my mother and my aunts and my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I walked in a work [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH] I used to call it, out of the ghetto every morning under SS guard.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I worked in a garage, in an automobile repair shop where there were SS cars being repaired and reconditioned.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was 1942.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was just about 15 years old, 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was always interested in cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a matter of fact, I volunteered for that job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One morning, we were standing up out at the work assignment place, approximately 500 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they asked, who knows something about automobiles?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I raised my hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said I do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They choose me to be part of that group to go out and work on cars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- there wasn't that much hardship on that particular job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then going back to the ghetto at night again, the hardship was so much worse, seeing the women suffer, and going to an environment which-- you know, like there was not going to be a tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This went on for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by that time, my sister was-- she was a year younger than I was, a year and a half, so she must've been about 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She also was going to work camp and she was sorting clothes for the German Army in a [NON-ENGLISH], where they were repairing and-- and sorting clothes for German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Ghetto life, looking back at it compared to what came afterwards, was easy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It wasn't comfortable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't pleasant.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
